reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact and Efficient Charging Power - Anker PowerPort Mini Dual Port Phone
reviews.reviewText: The Anker PowerPort Mini Dual Port Phone Charger has been a total game-changer for my charging needs! This compact powerhouse delivers exceptional charging performance and has quickly become an indispensable part of my daily routine.The first thing that caught my attention was its size. The charger is incredibly compact and lightweight, making it perfect for travel or on-the-go charging. Despite its small form factor, it packs a powerful punch, capable of charging two devices simultaneously at full speed.The dual-port feature is a fantastic convenience, allowing me to charge my phone and tablet simultaneously without any loss of charging speed. It significantly reduces the number of chargers I need to carry around and keeps all my devices powered up without any hassle.The charging speed is impressive! The PowerIQ technology automatically detects the connected device's power requirements and optimizes the charging output accordingly. I noticed a considerable reduction in charging time compared to other chargers I've used in the past.Moreover, the build quality of the Anker PowerPort Mini is top-notch. The robust construction gives me confidence that it will withstand the rigors of daily use, and the foldable plug design ensures that it stays compact and protected when not in use.Safety is always a concern when it comes to charging devices, but with Anker's MultiProtect technology, I feel at ease. The charger provides protection against overcharging, overheating, and short circuits, ensuring my devices are charged safely.Whether I'm at home, in the office, or traveling, the Anker PowerPort Mini Dual Port Phone Charger has become an essential part of my charging setup. Its efficiency, convenience, and reliable performance make it stand out from the competition.In conclusion, if you're looking for a compact, powerful, and safe phone charger, the Anker PowerPort Mini is the way to go. It delivers on its promises and has made charging my devices a breeze. I couldn't be happier with my purchase from Amazon, and I wholeheartedly recommend the Anker PowerPort Mini Dual Port Phone Charger to anyone in need of a reliable and efficient charging solution.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Reliable and convenient
reviews.reviewText: I have a bunch of these, as well as other Anker products, and never had an issue. These are not super speed chargers, nor is that why I bought them. Have a couple plugged in the kitchen outlets, and a couple in a go bag for vacations and such. These days, everything needs to charge, phones, headsets, work headsets, and many other devices. Far better than your checkout counter chargers, which I have had to buy in a pinch, and always seem to fit loosely in outlets, these do not have that problem. Now I have enough of these spread around, including one in my truck as a just in case on the road, that I am ready for any charging need where ever I may be. Being able to fold in the prongs makes them take up less room, though they are compact anyways.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One was defective
reviews.reviewText: Update to my review. I called customer service and explained about what had happened, and they were very helpful. Are sending new product to replace defective one at no charge and I don’t even have to send old one back!Very courteous and helpful. Have updated my rating from 2 stars to 5.I ordered the 2 pack of these wall charger outlets, and one of them worked perfectly, the other was defective. The first one worked great, charged devices very quickly.I tried the other, and all the device would do is flash very quickly between charging and not charging. I tried it on different devices and different outlets in my home, and same thing.I have used Anker products for years, and have never had a problem with them working flawlessly. But I have to say that I am disappointed with these. Since it happened immediately out of the box, it must have left the factory this way. I would think quality control would have caught this defect.
Cumple con las especificaciones, se calienta un poco pero puedo cargar 2 equipos tranquilamente.

I bought this specifically because of how small it is, and not because of charging power. However it is still a powerful charger with 5V 2.4A output for a single device. I already have one capable of doing 5V 2.4A for two devices, but it's larger than this one. As a repeat Anker customer I had high expectations and as usual I wasn't disappointed. Looks, feels, and performs great. Zero issues and works exactly how I want/need it to. It's also quite affordable especially considering its output and quality. The price is even better considering the one or two times I've used the Anker warranty I didn't wait long at all, and they simply replaced the item, no hassle whatsoever.

I bought this charger to charge my milwaukee usb batteries. It provides enough power to charge 2 batteries at the same time at the full rate. It is approved for use in canada and usa, so it is safe to leave plugged in. It is also very compact, so it takes almost no space when traveling.
Decía paquete de dos y solo me llegó uno.
